      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/755/068/original/4f481d9d-5a8f-447e-8ee4-0e619cb533b0.png" srcset="" alt="Open Settings" height="275" width="158">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_67494F00-22D0-0135-D40E-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Settings</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_course_details" data-step-uuid="2efcdaf2-6ef9-406b-b2f5-877d06ffae84">
